dc_title_s: Carte de Nigritie et Guinee; par P. du Val d'Abbeville, geographe du Roy.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Shows western Africa and the west coast of central Africa south to Luanda, Angola. I. Somer sculp. 1 map: hand col.; 38 x 54 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
